The Deciem purchase
was perhaps Lauder=E2=80=99s smartest deal this century: The Ordinary, its =
top brand, is a perennial bright spot in an otherwise lagging portfolio. In=
deed, Deciem was one of few revenue drivers (besides Le Labo) that instille=
d confidence both internally and among Wall Street analysts. Starting in Ja=
nuary, however, Kilner will be shifting into an advisory capacity=E2=80=94s=
he=E2=80=99ll work on people and culture, bigger-picture initiatives, and s=
trategy, which will surely include addressing an industry-wide softening in=
 skincare. Jesper Rasmussen, current global general manager and senior vice=
 president of Deciem, will be elevated to global brand president. Kilner co=
mmunicated the changes via email and during a team meeting at Deciem=E2=80=
=99s headquarters.

The news couldn=E2=80=99t have come at a more dramatic time for ELC. The La=
uder family is still reeling from Jane and William=E2=80=99s behind-the-sce=
nes internecine blood feud, which suddenly and intentionally became
extremely public ( https://puck.news/the-estee-lauder-blood-sacrifice/?utm_=
campaign=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F20%2F24%29&utm_content=3DLine+S=
heet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F18%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=
=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) last week. But I=E2=80=99m t=
old that Kilner, who is in her mid-30s, had been contemplating a change for=
 some time. After all, she=E2=80=99s also one of the few remaining founders=
 at the conglomerate: Jo Malone left in 2006, Bobbi Brown left in 2016, Too=
 Faced=E2=80=99s Jerrod Blandino and Jeremy Johnson left in 2022, and Fr=C3=
=A9d=C3=A9ric Malle left last June. Most have since started other beauty li=
nes. =E2=80=9C[Kilner] had three choices: to stay as is, to fully walk away=
, or a hybrid of the two,=E2=80=9D explained a source close to Deciem. =E2=
=80=9CPart of the reason she didn=E2=80=99t want to fully walk away was bec=
ause you can already feel the difference with St=C3=A9phane.=E2=80=9D

